HEADWORD: Anserine
<hw>An"ser*ine</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>anserinus</ets>, fr. <ets>anser</ets> a goose.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
